# Drop font files in this folder. Filenames must match exactly:
#
#   Recoleta-Regular.otf
#   Recoleta-Medium.otf
#   Recoleta-SemiBold.otf
#   Recoleta-Bold.otf
#   Recoleta-Black.otf
#   AirbnbCerealBook.ttf
#   AirbnbCerealMedium.ttf
#   AirbnbCerealBold.ttf
#   AirbnbCerealExtraBold.ttf
#
# They are served at /fonts/<filename> and referenced via @font-face in
# src/app/mission-matrix.css. Until they exist, the page falls back to
# Fraunces (for Recoleta) and Inter/system sans (for Cereal).
